The cat is sitting on my [..].
There are five [..] on my desk.
I have two [..].
They are riding their [..].
We have a [..].
How many [..] do you have in your bag?
My mother has a new [..].
There are three windows in the [..].
Susan has four [..].
There is one [..] on the floor.
The cat is sitting on my bed.
There are five pencils on my desk.
I have two sisters.
They are riding their bikes.
We have a dog.
How many books do you have in your bag?
My mother has a new computer.
There are three windows in the room.
Susan has four posters.
There is one pen on the floor.

